# Employee Management System (GraphQL API)
# Name: - Krishna Thakkar
# Student Id: - 101398578

This project is developed as part of **COMP3133 Assignment 1**.  
It is a **GraphQL-based Employee Management System** built using **Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Apollo Server,Express-validator**.

---

##  Features
- **User Authentication** (Signup & Login with JWT)
- **Employee Management** (CRUD Operations)
- **GraphQL API** for flexible data fetching
- **MongoDB Database (Mongoose Models)**
- **Validation & Error Handling**

